def: A manner of acting or of writing peculiar to, or characteristicof, Dr. Johnson. [Written also Johnsonism.]
The act, or art, of causing animals to produce tallow; also,the property in animals of producing tallow.
Pertaining to, or consisting of, entrochites, or the joints ofencrinites; -- used of a kind of stone or marble.
Of or pertaining to Bactria in Asia.-- n.
A fabulous deity supposed to dwell in, and preside over, somebody of water.
